    "Title": "~mission(ReputationRank) Rank - ~mission(CargoGradeToken) Cargo Haul",
    "DisplayTitle": "Junior Rank - Small Cargo Haul",
    "Description": "Hi,\n\nHurston is requesting that we prioritize pick ups from the local mining facilities to free up space for what they\u2019re extracting. Here\u2019s everywhere you need to go:  \n\nPICK UP LOCATIONS (ANY ORDER)\n\n~mission(MultiToSingleToken)\n\nOnce collected, everything needs to get to a freight elevator at <EM4>~mission(Destination|Address)</EM4>. They've said that all the containers will be at most <EM4>~mission(MissionMaxSCUSize)</EM4> in size. Sound like something you could handle? \n\nBy the way, we strongly encourage contractors to bring a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> along.   \n\n~mission(Contractor|SignOff)\n\nChase Hewitt\nJr. Logistics Coordinator\nCovalex Shipping  \n'Anything you need, anywhere you need it.'\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nCovalex Shipping is a limited liability corporation. To encourage timely deliveries and prevent fraud on cargo hauls, Covalex Shipping will set a delivery time limit and upon expiration, any undelivered cargo will be considered stolen and treated as such. Total payment will be prorated according to the percentage of cargo successfully delivered.",
    "DisplayDescription": "Hi,\n\nHurston is requesting that we prioritize pick ups from the local mining facilities to free up space for what they\u2019re extracting. Here\u2019s everywhere you need to go:  \n\nPICK UP LOCATIONS (ANY ORDER)\n\n- Freight elevator at <EM4>[Location|Address]</EM4>\n- Freight elevator at <EM4>[Location1|Address]</EM4>\n\nOnce collected, everything needs to get to a freight elevator at <EM4>[Destination|Address]</EM4>. They've said that all the containers will be at most <EM4>4 SCU</EM4> in size. Sound like something you could handle? \n\nBy the way, we strongly encourage contractors to bring a <EM4>handheld tractor beam</EM4> along.   \n\n[Contractor|SignOff]\n\nChase Hewitt\nJr. Logistics Coordinator\nCovalex Shipping  \n'Anything you need, anywhere you need it.'\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\nCovalex Shipping is a limited liability corporation. To encourage timely deliveries and prevent fraud on cargo hauls, Covalex Shipping will set a delivery time limit and upon expiration, any undelivered cargo will be considered stolen and treated as such. Total payment will be prorated according to the percentage of cargo successfully delivered.",
